column5: So I was at a Jack and Jill party and there was a raffle table with $25 bass pro gift cards.  So I bought $20 worth of raffle tickets and entered them all in the table with the gift cards and won 3 times for a total of $75.  Made my day as today I went and bought some new goodies
help out some friends and get some swag. Good on you.
Don't you love it when a plan comes together?
